Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.50,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.05,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.64,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.21,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.22,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.14,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.56,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:56.03,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:00.86,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.74,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.83,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.17,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.15,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has been separated from his crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:23.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and is heading for Navy HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.39,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,in order to rescue his captured brother, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:33.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Now, only three hours remain before the execution of Portgas D. Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Time of the Showdown Approaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's Mightiest Battle Formation is Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.84,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.56,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:54.37,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours left...  I wonder if Whitebeard's already shown himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:58.01,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...  Are you sure he'll show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.97,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this is Whitebeard, he's gotten pretty old by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.04,Main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.10,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He's a relic from before the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.66,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably gone senile by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.20,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,He's been quiet these last few years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.49,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,How can you guys be so blasé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.24,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone to underestimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:24.15,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Navy HQ has assembled their entire force against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:29.28,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Whitebeard will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.74,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,So, if he does appear, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:36.04,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?  I sure don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.86,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He's been around for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.92,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think Navy HQ can be defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.91,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,No pirate could win against the forces of Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.47,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.50,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, about 20 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:04.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirate Gold Lion Shiki invaded Marineford and destroyed half of Navy HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.88,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it could be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:14.15,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of who wins, there's gonna be heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.08,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be best if he didn't show...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:23.96,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to happen is a successful execution without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:34.20,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Hey!  I want some booze!  Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.90,Main,Salesman,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm gonna work the pub on a day like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.74,Main,Salesman,0000,0000,0000,,War might break out, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.60,Main,Salesman,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!  If the world's still here tomorrow, I'll open the pub then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.96,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, just sell me some booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:49.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we're the ones facing execution here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.98,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta have a drink to endure this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:58.54,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't think of him as just some old guy.  He's as strong as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:05.92,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,We saw him a year ago, he was just sitting there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.13,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,and we gave up all hope in our own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.84,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is Whitebeard really such a terrifying pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.75,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Even the kids know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.68,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,They're singing about him while jumping rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:27.52,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate Whitebeard, scarier than the Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.86,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:34.93,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this world headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.15,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,On the island of Navy HQ, Marineford...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:52.64,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,there is a village where the marines' families live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:08.89,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All the citizens have been ordered to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,From their new haven in the Sabaody Archipelago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:21.11,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the citizens eagerly watch the execution via monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.88,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Reporters and cameramen have gathered from all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:33.71,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to watch and keep the rest of the world informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.81,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Navy HQ has put all their forces into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.06,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.  And I'm sure Whitebeard knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.73,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,So, will he really show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:52.06,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All the Navy ships sent out to scout have been sunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.74,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has seen any trace of Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The tension at Marineford keeps building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:08.88,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Less than three hours remain before the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:29.02,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!  Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:37.11,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more than just the execution of a single pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:43.13,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how much this will affect the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.99,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:55.50,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of this, and as such, you carry a huge responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.10,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.89,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You!  Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.65,Main,Marine Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Show no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:54.16,Main,Marine Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, only three hours remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.26,Main,Marine Commander,0000,0000,0000,,then all of this will be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:02.11,Main,Marines,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:09.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In all, more than 100,000 marines have gathered from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:16.61,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty battleships encircle the crescent-shaped bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:21.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and within the bay, countless cannons are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:26.12,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The front row of the troops can be seen from the port...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.28,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,including the five rogues who could decide the outcome of this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.19,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,members of the Seven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.88,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.26,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,the Admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.84,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel so intimidated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:14.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Below the execution platform, Navy HQ's most powerful combat force stand guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:17.13,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The three Navy Admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.26,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.70,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,all the world's forces of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.97,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,await the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.71,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent them from rescuing Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.97,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.64,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We will definitely live life without regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.96,Thoughts,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.70,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, we will set out to sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.46,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,and live life the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.91,Thoughts,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,With more freedom than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:17.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:25.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.30,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Jinbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.32,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the Gate of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.59,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.56,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're actually pretty late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.80,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind had been more favorable, we would have arrived sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.10,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.84,Flashbacks,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.46,Flashbacks,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we open the Gates of Justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.24,Flashbacks,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,you will not be able to reach Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:07.32,Flashbacks,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,nor will you be able to escape from the Tarai Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:12.05,Flashbacks,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,There is no sea to escape to, nor anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.28,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are we going to get through that gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.08,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,My men!  It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.62,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Time for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.85,Main,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,TIME FOR CAPTAIN BUGGY TO RULE THE WORLD!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.50,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.34,Main,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about Navy HQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.39,Main,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.10,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Who will become the Pirate King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.01,Main,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,CAPTAIN BUGGY!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.35,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:54.16,Main,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy!  Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:32.13,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!  There's Fire-Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:42.79,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,That's...  the man who might cause a war that changes the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:51.80,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,He also holds the fate of the world in his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.64,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make an announcement.  That okay with you, Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.75,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.  I'll be down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.35,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Give us some room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.26,Main,Executioners,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.05,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.93,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.21,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the Snail Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.93,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,I have an announcement for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.00,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Portgas D. Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:13.84,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,The death of this man today, holds great significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.39,Main,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.56,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Women are supposed to be sympathetic at times like this, Tsuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.93,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.  Tell me the name of your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.41,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,His father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:37.15,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.24,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,My father is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.50,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:50.41,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,It is!  My father is Whitebeard!  I have no other father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:55.55,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Years ago, we put all our resources into searching for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:20:00.42,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,We suspected that he might have a child on a certain island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:05.99,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,We relied entirely on this possibility, and Cipher Pol's vague information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.39,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Children who had just been born...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.35,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Children who were about to be born...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:16.82,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,We thoroughly investigated all the mothers but we couldn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.65,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose that was to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.76,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother risked her life to deliver you safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:27.33,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,She performed a special trick, which she pulled off through sheer willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:37.94,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,She deceived our eyes...  No, the eyes of the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:42.26,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,In South Blue, there is an island called Baterilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:48.47,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother's name is Portgas D. Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:55.43,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,She managed to defy common sense with sheer willpower to protect her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:21:00.32,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,She carried her child in her womb for 20 whole months.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.70,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:10.87,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,She used all of her strength and as soon as she gave birth to you, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.82,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,A year and three months after the father's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:22.84,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,a child was born, carrying the blood of the most evil man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.93,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,That child was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:33.77,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.92,Flashbacks,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,A newborn child bears no sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:46.70,Flashbacks,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:50.17,Flashbacks,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.80,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:02.93,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,the Pirate King, Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:29.41,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Fire-Fist Ace...  is Gold Roger's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.26,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,This is huge news!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:40.12,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Call the main office right away!  We're releasing an extra for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.07,Main,Reporter 2,0000,0000,0000,,So, it still lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:48.72,Main,Reporter 2,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:56.22,Main,Reporter 2,0000,0000,0000,,The blood of the Pirate King lives on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.87,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of Ace's origin has been revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:18.94,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His father Roger's feelings, and his mother Rouge's strong will lay behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:24.21,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And, at Marineford, Whitebeard's fleet silently approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.14,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Enormous Fleet Appears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Invasion of the Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:31.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
